T02TD3539E:179b-1: parna sha ba ri s'a dha nam /
T02TD3539E:179b-3: ri khrod lo ma can gyi sgrub thabs /
T02TD3539E:179b-4: 'phags ma ri khrod ma lo ma can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3539E:179b-5: sngon du gsungs pa'i cho gas stong pa nyid bsgoms pa'i rjes la sna tshogs padma dang zla ba la gnas pa'i pam yig ljang gu la skyes pa'i ri khrod ma lo ma can sku mdog ljang gu zhal gsum pa /
T02TD3539E:179b-9: dkar po dag g-yas dang g-yon gyi zhal lo //
T02TD3539E:179b-10: phyag g-yas pa gsum na rdo rje dang /
T02TD3539E:179b-13: phyag g-yon pa gsum na gzhu bkang ba dang /
T02TD3539E:179b-15: sdigs mdzub dang bcas pa'i zhags pa bsnams pa /
T02TD3539E:179b-16: zhal khro ba dang bcas shing bzhad pa /
T02TD3539E:179b-18: phreng ba bcings shing stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs can cung zad lto ba 'phyang ba /
T02TD3539E:180a-1: 'og tu ma lus pa'i nad dang /
T02TD3539E:180a-3: don yod grub pas dbu brgyan pa'i bdag nyid du skad cig gis bskyed nas sngags bzlas par bya'o //
T02TD3539E:180a-4: aom pi sh'a tsi parna sha ba ri sarba m'a ri pra sha ma ni h'um phat /
T02TD3539E:180a-5: ri khrod lo ma can gyi sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
